Package: reconstruction2D
Title: Reconstruction of 2D Shapes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("St√©phane", "Laurent", , "laurent_step@outlook.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Given a set of 2D points, possibly hampered by noise and
    outliers, the main function of this package returns a set of segments
    and isolated points that approximate the input. The algorithm is
    performed by the 'C++' library 'CGAL' (<https://www.cgal.org/>).
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/stla/reconstruction2D
BugReports: https://github.com/stla/reconstruction2D/issues
Imports: 
    Rcpp,
    stats
LinkingTo: 
    BH,
    Rcpp,
    RcppCGAL,
    RcppEigen
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
SystemRequirements: C++17, gmp, mpfr
